Interface Monitor.Result

    An interface holds the result executed by a task.

    • Method Detail

      • name

        String name()
        Name of the result. This attribute may be used in namespace as path. For instance, when publishing to ZooKeeper, it writes to "/monitor//metrics/jvm" where jvm is the name provided by Result.name() function to identify the metrics record. So ideally name should be given without space e.g. `jvm', instead of `Java virtual machine'.
        Returns:
        name.

        Returns:
        Destination in array.

        Returns:
